# Python: Use uv

- Prefer `uv` for Python project management (`uv sync`, `uv add`, `uv remove`).
- Run Python and tools via `uv run` (e.g. `uv run python`, `uv run pytest`).
- Do not default to bare `pip` / `venv` when `uv` is available.
